msgctxt "104_Guessing the Number on One Die"
msgid ""
"You can bet on what number will show on one of the two dice.\r\n"
"If you guess right, you can earn even more tags by simply guessing odd or "
"even."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116_Guessing the Number on One Die"
msgid ""
"You can also bet on which numbers will show on both dice.\r\n"
"If you guess right, you get all of the money in the current pot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128_Guessing the Number on One Die"
msgid ""
"However, you must wager 20 percent of the betting limit in order to make "
"your bet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140_Guessing the Number on One Die"
msgid ""
"To play against the house, first place any bet. Guess right, and the tags "
"you win become your new bet against the house.\r\n"
"Your next turn you will again guess either odd or even. Guess right, and "
"you win twice the amount of tags you bet.\r\n"
"Up to five rolls are possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152_Guessing the Number on One Die"
msgid ""
"Cho-han is a dice-rolling game where you guess if the total value of a pair "
"of dice will be odd or even."
msgstr ""